OL,3,CHarry echoes mother's words as he
OL,4,Cgives message to Trump and Putin from
OL,5,CUkraine
OL,7,FPrince Harry has issued a message
OL,8,Fdirectly to two presidents - Trump and
OL,9,FPutin - about the war in Ukraine.
OL,11,FHe was speaking in Kyiv at the start
OL,12,Fof an unannounced visit in which he is
OL,13,Fmeeting senior members of the
OL,14,FUkrainian military and some of the
OL,15,Fthousands of soldiers who have been
OL,16,Fseriously wounded in the conflict.
OL,18,FHe also defended his visit to Ukraine,
OL,19,Fsaying he was "not here as a
OL,20,Fpolitician".
OL,26,@{D@OOU|D@KO]
