OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776960675
OL,3,CHarry echoes mother's words as he
OL,4,Cgives message to Trump and Putin from
OL,5,CUkraine
OL,7,FThe Duke of Sussex was invited to
OL,8,Fdeliver the keynote speech at the Kyiv
OL,9,FSecurity Forum which is taking place
OL,10,Fdespite ongoing Russian attacks on
OL,11,FUkraine.
OL,13,FPrince Harry told the Russian
OL,14,Fpresident that there is "still a
OL,15,Fmoment, now, to stop this war".
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@vD@YOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776960675
OL,3,CHarry echoes mother's words as he
OL,4,Cgives message to Trump and Putin from
OL,5,CUkraine
OL,7,F"Years into this war", Harry told
OL,8,FPresident Putin, "with immense losses
OL,9,Fand limited gains, it is increasingly
OL,10,Fclear that this path offers no victor
OL,11,F- only more loss."
OL,13,FHe added: "President Putin, no nation
OL,14,Fbenefits from the continued loss of
OL,15,Flife we are witnessing."
OL,17,FHe gave the speech hours after
OL,18,Fstepping off an overnight train from
OL,19,FPoland and arriving at Kyiv's central
OL,20,Fstation at 8am.
OL,26,@sD@RO]wD@XO]
