OL,3,CHarry echoes mother's words as he
OL,4,Cgives message to Trump and Putin from
OL,5,CUkraine
OL,7,FThe prince did not mention Donald
OL,8,FTrump by name but he said he had a
OL,9,Fmessage for the "American leadership".
OL,11,FHarry said the US - his adopted
OL,12,Fcountry - has a "singular role" in
OL,13,Fthis conflict because, when Ukraine
OL,14,Fagreed to give up its nuclear weapons,
OL,15,FAmerica had pledged to protect
OL,16,FUkraine's borders and its sovereignty.
OL,26,@qD@QOUqD@eO]tD@QOUtD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776960675
OL,3,CHarry echoes mother's words as he
OL,4,Cgives message to Trump and Putin from
OL,5,CUkraine
OL,7,FHe told the Trump administration:
OL,8,F"This is a moment for American
OL,9,Fleadership ` a moment for America to
OL,10,Fshow that it can honour its
OL,11,Finternational treaty obligations - not
OL,12,Fout of charity, but out of its
OL,13,Fenduring role in global security and
OL,14,Fstrategic stability."
OL,16,FHarry will undertake engagements with
OL,17,Fthe the Invictus Games foundation he
OL,18,Ffounded after he left the British Army.
OL,26,@vD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
