FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776960675
OL,3,CHarry echoes mother's words as he
OL,4,Cgives message to Trump and Putin from
OL,5,CUkraine
OL,7,FThere is a staggering number of
OL,8,FUkrainian soldiers with life-changing
OL,9,Finjuries. It runs into the many tens
OL,10,Fof thousands.
OL,12,FHarry will also see the work of the de-
OL,13,Fmining charity, The Halo Trust, which
OL,14,Fis close to his heart because of his
OL,15,Fmother's work with them in Angola
OL,16,Fshortly before she died.
OL,18,FPrincess Diana was famously filmed
OL,19,Fwalking through a cleared minefield
OL,20,Fwith a flak jacket and visor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
