FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1776960675
OL,3,CHarry echoes mother's words as he
OL,4,Cgives message to Trump and Putin from
OL,5,CUkraine
OL,7,FHarry echoed the words of his mother
OL,8,Fin his speech to the security
OL,9,Fconference.
OL,11,FHe said: "I am not here as a
OL,12,Fpolitician.
OL,14,F"I am here as a soldier who
OL,15,Funderstands service, as a humanitarian
OL,16,Fwho has seen the human cost of
OL,17,Fconflict, and as a friend of Ukraine
OL,18,Fwho believes the world must not grow
OL,19,Fused to this war or numb to its
OL,20,Fconsequences."
OL,26,@sD@JOU|D@NO]
